{"tid":2299174,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"好奇一問身邊有冇同事中招？","createTime":"2020-11-24T14:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T14:38:15.000Z","uid":339084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5232fddc94f772a40f418923d95d3cecfedb00d4","tid":2299174,"uid":339084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"屋企大廈有人確診所以公司安排隔離十四日，<br />\n唔知番到公司同事會點睇，<br />\n本身都唔係同佢地太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人身邊有同事中招之後好番？<br />\n會唔會俾人係背後指指點點？"},{"pid":"74ed5217f1a4cea45d0802681952234e9981fb00","tid":2299174,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n係住嗰橦大廈有人奶野"},{"pid":"6a9a7c969518421d9e81acdf47cfa51daa8e0baf","tid":2299174,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:30:55.000Z","msg":"一定會<br />\n冇中都會當你怪物咁睇"},{"pid":"75815ed4304b81e2bd371ffecaf59bd8dafb5002","tid":2299174,"uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"有同事中招，係上一波<br />\n但佢無咩事，係果排無左味覺<br />\n初頭就好好奇，都有少少擔心會唔會仲有病毒，但而家正常返工都返左2個幾月，間唔時都一齊食飯，所有同事都無當咩一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為好返後真係同以前完全無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}